    <j.0:initiated_by rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EP"/>
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="fr">The European Parliament proposed 48 amendments of which the Commission accepted 13 as a whole and 6 in part. The amendments accepted are varied, but include those which refer to the link between the ESF and the European Employment Strategy, clarify the importance of partnership - particularly involving NGOs - in the Structural Funds, and relate to equal opportunities between men and women. Cette proposition a été modifiée suite à l'avis du PE du 19/11/1998.</j.0:comment>
    <j.0:event_date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1998-11-19</j.0:event_date>
